    <h2>What Else is Nearby? The Air and Space Museum!</h2>
    <p>
    The <%= link_to "Udvar-Hazy Air and Space Museum", "http://www.nasm.si.edu/UdvarHazy/" %>, 
    is a great place to spend the Sunday after RubyNation.  
    There are lots of wonderful, historical aircraft on display, including
    the Enola Gay B-29 Superfortress, the Space Shuttle Enterprise, 
    the Lockheed SR-71 Blackbird, and a Concorde supersonic airliner.
    </p>

    <p>
    The Museum is just up the road, near Dulles Airport.  
    Well worth a Sunday morning visit after RubyNation.
